Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:28.22,Insert_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(200,200)}現今交疊的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.88,Insert_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(200,200)}將繪出的祈願相連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:39.94,Insert_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(200,200)}把那地平線 飛越
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙已經找到…並且毀掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家出來看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪雅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 爸爸 發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…在喝茶的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天文明也說會早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
